title: #92Noon! Friday Feast
description: PA & Charch! Adam Thielen opens the show, followed by NFL analyst Ross Tucker, then Mike Florio finishes a busy first hour. In the final hour, Kevin Gorg and Brian Arrigoni are in studio to chat horses and hockey!
